<bibRefCitation author="Nogueira" box="[158,389,186,209]" pageId="2" pageNumber="66" refString="Nogueira, A. A., J. P. P. Pena-Barbosa, E. M. Venticinque &amp; A. D. Brescovit. (2011). The spider genus Chrysometa (Araneae, Tetragnathidae) from the Pico da Neblina and Serra do Tapirapeco mountains (Amazonas, Brazil): new species, new records, diversity and distribution along two altitudinal gradients. Zootaxa, 2772, 33 - 51." type="journal article" year="2011">
Nogueira 
<emphasis box="[266,319,186,209]" italics="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="66">et al.</emphasis>
, 
<number box="[332,389,186,209]" pageId="2" pageNumber="66" value="2011.0">2011</number>
</bibRefCitation>
).
</paragraph>
